hip + practice building RE ownership.</strong> FL no-state-income-tax preserves substantial qualifying — vs California (13.3%) saves $147K annually on combined $1.13M income; vs New York (10.9%) saves $121K annually. Multi-decade lifetime preservation $3M-$5M+. $2.85M Conventional Jumbo close in 45 days. <strong>The pattern: DPT brings multi-clinic + RE + athletic consulting complexity, Stairway brings B3-3.4-02 multi-entity Form 1084 + B3-3.2-01 self-employed + comprehensive physical therapy continuity narrative craft.</strong></p>
